-- Bank of Ghana Sees Cedi Stabilizing in Fourth Quarter, Joy Says
-- B y   P a u l i n e   B a x
-- 2012-07-04T09:09:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-04/bank-of-ghana-sees-cedi-stabilizing-in-fourth-quarter-joy-says.html
The  Bank of Ghana  said the currency
will probably stabilize from the fourth quarter as proceeds from
cocoa exports begin flowing in, Accra-based Joy FM reported,
citing Deputy Governor Millison Narh.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Pauline Bax in Accra at 
